metadata.name: CYBERWAVE
metadata.description:
Dot has created a synthwave-inspired sample pack featuring dreamy chord progressions, driving basslines, and ethereal vocal samples. The pack offers a unique and versatile collection of sounds perfect for creating a soundtrack for your next video game or VR experience. The sample pack is designed to bring a sense of nostalgia and futurism to your productions.
